@Node Description "Description"

  Description
  ===========

    The Hack door is called by the fontend door when a user is not allowed
    to login for some reason.   This door gives the user the chance to
    page the sysop or leave a comment.

@EndNode

@Node Installation "Installation"

  Installation
  ============

    Included as part of the default HydraBBS setup.

@EndNode

@Node SystemOptions "SystemOptions"

  System Options
  ==============

    None

@EndNode

@Node CmdLineOptions "CmdLineOptions"

  Command Line Options
  ====================

    <Reason> <Username>

    Where reason is one of:

      PSWD  -  If the user failed a password check
      TIME  -  If the user has no time left
      LOCK  -  If the user's account is locked out.

    Example Parameters

    PSWD Hydra

@EndNode

@Node ScreensDisplayed "Screens Displayed"

  Screens Displayed
  =================

    None

  Special Screens Displayed
  =========================

    Hack_PSWD  -  If the user failed a password check
    Hack_TIME  -  If the user has no time left
    Hack_LOCK  -  If the user's account is locked out.
    Hack_BYE   -  When the hack door quits.


@EndNode

@Node DoorsCalled "Doors Called"

  Doors Called
  ============

    User Doors:

    O - Pager door, no paramaters
    C - Comment door, no paramaters

@EndNode

